'''何塞·马利亚·伊波利托·菲格雷斯·费雷尔'''（'''José María Hipólito Figueres Ferrer'''，{{bd|1906年|9月25日|1990年|6月8日|catIdx=Figueres Ferrer, Jose}}），[[哥斯达黎加|哥斯达黎加]]溫和的社會主義政治人物，曾经三次出任[[哥斯达黎加总统|哥斯达黎加总统]]。

== 人物经历 ==

出生于哥斯达黎加[[阿拉胡埃拉省|阿拉胡埃拉省]][[聖拉蒙區|聖拉蒙區]]，1942年4月，他因为在电台发表演讲抨击卡尔德隆政府的腐败而被迫流亡[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]，1944年5月卡尔德隆卸任后，菲格雷斯得以返回哥斯达黎加，并在自己的咖啡园内建立了武装队伍{{link-en|加勒比军团|Caribbean Legion}}，开始筹划推翻{{link-es|民族共和党|Partido Republicano Nacional}}领导的哥斯达黎加政府。<ref name=ref1>{{cite news | title=Costa Rica's Fierce Pacifist | work=The New York Times | date=June 1990 | url=https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/17/opinion/costa-rica-s-fierce-pacifist.html | issn=0362-4331 | accessdate=2022-03-13 | archive-date=2022-03-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220312043854/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/17/opinion/costa-rica-s-fierce-pacifist.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ref3>{{cite news | last=Oliver | first=Myrna | title=Jose Figueres, 82; Former Costa Rican President | work=Los Angeles Times | date=June 1990 | url=http://articles.latimes.com/1990-06-09/news/mn-591_1_costa-rican-government | issn=0458-3035 | accessdate=2022-03-13 | archive-date=2015-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723041322/http://articles.latimes.com/1990-06-09/news/mn-591_1_costa-rican-government | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ref6>[http://www.livejournal.com/users/bailey83221/45020.html "How Costa Rica Lost Its Military"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.livejournal.com/users/bailey83221/45020.html |date=20220217074014 }} citing:
*{{cite book | author=Ameringer, Charles D. | title=Don Pepe: A political biography of José Figueres of Costa Ricas | publisher=University of New Mexico Press | year=1978 | isbn=978-0-8263-0480-3 | url=https://archive.org/details/donpepepolitical00amer }}
*{{harvnb | Bird | 1984 }}
*{{harvnb | Bell | 1971 }}
*{{cite journal | last1=Høivik | first1=Tord | last2=Aas | first2=Solveig | title=Demilitarization in Costa Rica: A Farewell to Arms? | journal=Journal of Peace Research | date=December 1981 | doi=10.1177/002234338101800403 | issn=0022-3433 | volume=18 | issue=4 | pages=333–350| s2cid=110377590 }}
*{{cite book | author=Jiménez, Iván Molina | title= Costa Rica: Historia de Costa Rica | url=https://archive.org/details/historiadecostar0000moli | publisher=Editorial de la Universidad de Costa Rica | year=1997 | isbn=978-9977-67-411-7}}</ref><ref name=ref8>{{cite news | last=Pace | first=Eric | title=Jose Figueres Ferrer Is Dead at 83; Led Costa Ricans to Democracy | work=The New York Times | date=June 1990 | url=https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/09/obituaries/jose-figueres-ferrer-is-dead-at-83-led-costa-ricans-to-democracy.html | issn=0362-4331 | accessdate=2022-03-13 | archive-date=2022-04-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220402150347/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/09/obituaries/jose-figueres-ferrer-is-dead-at-83-led-costa-ricans-to-democracy.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ref9>{{cite journal | last1=Delpar | first1=Helen | last2=Perez | first2=Louis A. | others=Benjamin Welles, Daniela Spenser, Friedrich E. Schuler, Maria Emilia Paz, Michael L. Krenn, Michael D. Gambone, Kyle Longley, James G. Blight, Peter Kornbluh, Lars Schoultz, Gilbert M. Joseph, Catherine C. LeGrand, Ricardo D. Salvatore (eds.) | title=Inter-American Relations and Encounters: Recent Directions in the Literature | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_latin-american-research-review_2000_35_3/page/155 | journal=Latin American Research Review | date=2000 | jstor=2692045 | issn=0023-8791 | volume=35 | issue=3 | page=155}}</ref>1948年，他率领[[民族解放党|哥斯大黎加民族解放軍]]在[[哥斯达黎加内战|哥斯达黎加内战]]中战胜政府军，成立了过渡性质的{{link-en|哥斯达黎加第二共和国执政委员会|Founding Junta of the Second Republic|执政委员会}}，自任执政委员会主席，并组织召开了{{link-en|1948年哥斯达黎加制宪会议|1948 Costa Rican Constituent Assembly election|制宪会议}}，<ref name=archi>{{cite news |title=Junta Fundadora de la Segunda República. 1948-1953 |url=http://www.archivonacional.go.cr/pdf/isadg_junta_fundadora.pdf |publisher=Archivo Nacional de Costa Rica |accessdate=30 July 2010 |archive-date=2014-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911113649/http://www.archivonacional.go.cr/pdf/isadg_junta_fundadora.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>制定了哥斯达黎加第二共和国宪法，废除军队。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.museocostarica.go.cr/boletin/noticias/142-la-abolici%C3%B3n-del-ej%C3%A9rcito-en-costa-rica-apuntes.html#sthash.Xr3XWvl6.dpbs|title=La Abolición del Ejército en Costa Rica, Apuntes|access-date=15 June 2018|last=Segura|first=Wendy|website=www.museocostarica.go.cr|language=es|journal=|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329222652/http://www.museocostarica.go.cr/boletin/noticias/142-la-abolici%C3%B3n-del-ej%C3%A9rcito-en-costa-rica-apuntes.html#sthash.Xr3XWvl6.dpbs|dead-url=no}}</ref>并將[[銀行|銀行]][[國有化|國有化]]，給予[[婦女|婦女]]和[[黑人|黑人]][[投票權|投票權]]。

其子[[何塞·玛丽亚·菲格雷斯|何塞·玛丽亚·菲格雷斯]]亦于1994-1998年出任哥斯达黎加总统。

